{
  "page": "Lord of Horn Hill",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of Horn Hill</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> is a title held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarly\" title=\"House Tarly\">House Tarly</a>, the ruler of <a href=\"/index.php/Horn_Hill\" title=\"Horn Hill\">Horn Hill</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Reach.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Reach and the location of Horn Hill\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Horn Hill\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/300px-The_Reach.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/450px-The_Reach.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/600px-The_Reach.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 56.7%; left: 43.3%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Horn Hill\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Horn Hill\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Horn Hill</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> and the location of Horn Hill\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Known_Lords_of_Horn_Hill\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Lords of Horn Hill</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Horn_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the reign of <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I Targaryen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly_(lord)\" title=\"Samwell Tarly (lord)\">Savage Sam Tarly</a> was among the <a href=\"/index.php/Marcher_lords\" title=\"Marcher lords\">marcher lords</a> who participated in the <a href=\"/index.php/Vulture_Hunt\" title=\"Vulture Hunt\">Vulture Hunt</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryens_kings:_aenys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryens_kings:_aenys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/49_AC\" title=\"49 AC\">49&#160;AC</a>, Lord Tarly was present at <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Wedding\" title=\"Golden Wedding\">wedding</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alan_Tarly\" title=\"Alan Tarly\">Alan Tarly</a> declared for Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, fighting and being taken captive in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_on_the_Honeywine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle on the Honeywine\">battle on the Honeywine</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Randyll_Tarly\" title=\"Randyll Tarly\">Randyll Tarly</a> commanded the vanguard of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Ashford\" title=\"Battle of Ashford\">Battle of Ashford</a>, where he killed <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Cafferen\" title=\"Lord Cafferen\">Lord Cafferen</a> and forced Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> to retreat. Randyll's liege, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a>, took credit for the victory, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Horn_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Horn_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord Randyll is among the lords that join their forces to <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>'s beneath <a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> After <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(299)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (299)\">Renly's death at Storm's End</a>, Lord Randyll rides back to Bitterbridge where he captures Renly's stores and puts many men to death, mainly <a href=\"/index.php/House_Florent\" title=\"House Florent\">Florent</a> men-at-arms, lest they go over to Stannis along with their lords.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> Randyll joins his liege lord, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">Tyrell</a>-<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> alliance at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup> where he commands the center of the host.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Horn_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord Randyll leaves the capital and march north towards <a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale\" title=\"Duskendale\">Duskendale</a> where he defeats the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">northern</a> army led by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Helman_Tallhart\" title=\"Helman Tallhart\">Helman Tallhart</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Robett_Glover\" title=\"Robett Glover\">Robett Glover</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup> He then captures <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Horn_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The timid and cowardly <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Maidenpool\" title=\"Lord of Maidenpool\">Lord of Maidenpool</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/William_Mooton\" title=\"William Mooton\">William Mooton</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup> does not dare confront Lord Randyll, who rules the town in all but name.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup> Lord Randyll arranges a <a href=\"/index.php/Betrothal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Betrothal\">betrothal</a> for his son and heir, <a href=\"/index.php/Dickon_Tarly\" title=\"Dickon Tarly\">Dickon Tarly</a>, to William's eldest daughter and heir, <a href=\"/index.php/Eleanor_Mooton\" title=\"Eleanor Mooton\">Eleanor Mooton</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Horn_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Randyll returns to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> upon receiving news of the arrest of <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a>. He receives custody of her and her cousins after swearing a holy oath to return them for trial. As part of Lord Regent <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a>'s efforts to assuage the men of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, Lord Tarly is named <a href=\"/index.php/Justiciar\" title=\"Justiciar\">justiciar</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">small council</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_17-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-17\">&#91;17&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Lords_of_Horn_Hill\">Known Lords of Horn Hill</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Horn_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Lords of Horn Hill\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly_(lord)\" title=\"Samwell Tarly (lord)\">Samwell Tarly</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_18-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-18\">&#91;18&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord Tarly, present at the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Wedding\" title=\"Golden Wedding\">Golden Wedding</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Donald_Tarly\" title=\"Donald Tarly\">Donald Tarly</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_19-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-19\">&#91;19&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alan_Tarly\" title=\"Alan Tarly\">Alan Tarly</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Randyll_Tarly\" title=\"Randyll Tarly\">Randyll Tarly</a>, the current Lord of Horn Hill.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Horn_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragotap